nst his mother. He consented to the divorce and prayed the court to grant him custody of the children. t later released them to her after embarrassing me in the market square. [NAN] Vanguard News Nigeria An Agege Grade ‘A’ Customary Court in Lagos also yesterday dissolved a 16-year-old marriage over battery, threat to life and fetish acts by the husband. December 11, 2012 In "News" A Customary Court sitting in Mapo in Ibadan, on Thursday dissolved a 15-year-old marriage between a mother of two, Olubunmi Faseyitan, and her husband, Kolawole, over ”witchcraft” suspicion. January 15, 2021 In "News" ABEOKUTA— A former chairman of Badagry Local Government Area of Lagos State, Babatunde Alabi, has approached an Ogun State High Court sitting in Isabo, Abeokuta seeking dissolution of his 33‑year‑old marriage to his wife, Modupe, over alleged negligence. June 20, 2014 In "News"